Package: simcostar
Type: Package
Title: Client for the SIMCOSTA Buoy Data API
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Eduardo", "Leoni", email = "e.leoni@gmail.com",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Download and cache oceanographic and meteorological buoy data
    from the SIMCOSTA platform (<https://simcosta.furg.br>). Provides
    incremental downloads with a local SQLite cache and coverage tracking
    so repeated queries only fetch missing time windows.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
Depends: R (>= 4.1.0)
Imports:
    cli,
    DBI,
    data.table,
    httr2,
    jsonlite,
    rlang,
    RSQLite
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    withr
Config/testthat/edition: 3
URL: https://github.com/leoniedu/simcostar
BugReports: https://github.com/leoniedu/simcostar/issues
